claim.claim-text:
14. A method for interfacing a machine controller with one or more of plural wireless networks distributed over a geographic area, the method comprising: 
integrating a wireless interface module with the machine controller, the wireless interface module having a wireless transceiver port; 
deploying the machine controller to a predetermined geographic location; 
determining one of the plural wireless networks as preferred for the geographic location; and 
removably coupling a wireless transceiver associated with the preferred wireless network to the wireless transceiver port.
